 white toga fastened with gold clips conceal the trunk of his body and his upper legs. White stoned pillars and houses reflect in his blue eyes  and the sound of water crashing down on water and flowing back in on itself echoes in the meadow.:: <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 11/26/01 10:00:16 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 238<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(11/27/01 10:45:01 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.tripod.com/~Poseidon64/poseidon3.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aftermath</span><hr size=1> ::His skin and shape shifts to that of a young, poor-looking mortal. He has slighty dark skin, brown eyes and short cropped black hair. The form he assumes is scrawny and he wears rags and his small, dirty feet are bare. The town is bustling with people. Fruit and clothes stands line the walls of the houses. People shout over each other to be heard. Carriages and carts with goods for bartering drawn by asses creak down the town lanes. Poseidon bumps into a thick set short man rushing by him and falls to the ground with a grunt. The man looks back at him and hurries along to wherever he was going not bothering to help him. He gets up and rubs a small scar that is on his elbow. Hundreds of faces look down into the streets from upstairs apartments and washed clothes are hung from clothes lines that extend from roof to roof. Poseidon notices a stand in which the merchant is selling small statues of their god Poseidon and other accessories that deal with the god. He smiles at his pleasure and walks over to a wall that is not crowded with people. He leans back  on it with his hands in his pockets and one ankle crossed over the other.:: <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=204.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showMessage?topicID=192.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.emailToFriend?topicID=202.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.threadControl?topicID=202.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/blueMoon/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=202.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=202.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub11.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="amazonsuniteamazonsunitescrollboard">Amazons Unite Scroll Board<option value="amazonsunitefrm32">The Mythical Odyssey<option value="amazonsunitefrm23">The Olympian Gods<option value="amazonsunitefrm15">Black Sea Tavern and Inn<option value="amazonsunitesistersofthemiscrya">Sisters of Themiscrya<option value="amazo